    • addToLinks

      void addToLinks(RecommendedInstance recommendedModelInstance, ModelInstance instance, Claimant claimant, double probability)
      Adds the connection of a recommended instance and a model instance to the state. If the model instance is already contained by the state it is extended. Elsewhere a new instance link is created
      Parameters:
      recommendedModelInstance - the recommended instance
      instance - the model instance
      probability - the probability of the link
